{"tid":1591943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣反暴政大片《返校》, 香港定於12月5日上映!","createTime":"2019-09-24T11:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T13:42:33.000Z","uid":134071,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9a0d65a616886249972ec005f340655808600022","tid":1591943,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:24:22.000Z","msg":"但新版海報無左原來香港發行商Screen Media HK (黃百鳴公司) 既標誌?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/DetentionMovieHK/photos/a.124689638912052/124689418912074/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDetentionMovieHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.124689638912052%2F124689418912074%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=32b0ccd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/DetentionMovieHK/photos/a.124689638912052/124689418912074/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n返校 Detention 電影-香港<br />\n&middot; 1 小時 &middot;<br />\n <br />\n要大家久等唔好意思！<br />\n<br />\n知道大家都對《返校》好期待，之前暫時收起係因為檔期有變，而家重開啦！《返校》將會係12月5日同香港觀眾見面，希望大家到時要多多捧場！<br />\n<br />\n#返校 #12月5日怨靈迴校<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/xUbFHWH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxUbFHWH.jpg&h=8da73a44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1825aa8a00295edf14912e6b4bb1de1d179016a4","tid":1591943,"uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:24:27.000Z","msg":"多謝連登仔馬德鐘 提供消息!<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜支持者們都不斷呼籲抵制白色恐怖電影《返校》, 但套戲既台灣票房依然勁收!<br />\n<br />\n影片預告... 好似講緊未來香港?<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cq0K2ipTaPM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCq0K2ipTaPM&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=37dbd0d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cq0K2ipTaPM</a>"},{"pid":"7855d3e4351836b2ba94ab460c8f94fec4eff04b","tid":1591943,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"644c3a01902141fdab75dba18e11e4070e61d065","tid":1591943,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:25:55.000Z","msg":"google cache:  Screen Media HK片單原本有《返校》<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/VPr6nSx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPr6nSx.jpg&h=fe2f6ae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在, Screen Media HK片單已刪去《返校》<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pictame.com/user/screenmediahk/followings/8666207205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pictame.com%2Fuser%2Fscreenmediahk%2Ffollowings%2F8666207205&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=701edece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.pictame.com/user/screenmediahk/followings/8666207205</a>"},{"pid":"5139b10f35bf594a09dffabb38ba4ab188977f66","tid":1591943,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e0e9d07c0fcc3fd1938b6cc81ce3e1f3e7e00b","tid":1591943,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"OLD NEWS<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190923/20773376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190923%2F20773376&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=ff8ace79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190923%2F20773376&h=b1fb1518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190923/20773376</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年09月23日<br />\n 《返校》講暴政 港上映無期<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】講述台灣1960年代白色恐怖時期的電影《返校》原定10月17日在香港上映，但電影突然被下架，香港發行商相關宣傳亦突然全被刪去，上映無期。大陸對此片亦大力封殺，惹起政治審查疑雲，影評人畢明不排除片商更改上映日期是出於政治考慮。<br />\n記者：陳詠恩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n驚悚電影《返校》由同名電子遊戲改編，以1962年的台灣為背景，由一段師生戀揭示台灣戒嚴時期學校充斥白色恐怖，讀禁書者被判叛國罪，言論自由受監控。電影9月20日在台灣上映後票房勁收，開畫票房創下台灣片八年來最佳紀錄，原定10月17日在香港上映，惟有網民發現電影檔期忽告「失蹤」，用作宣傳的facebook專頁「返校 Detention 電影-香港」被刪去。<br />\n<br />\n疑政治審查<br />\n<br />\n香港電台主持人周偉基指出，從台灣電影圈朋友中得知，《返校》的香港映期已被「技術性延遲」，現在上映日期未定，被網民質疑是港版「白色恐怖」。<br />\n<br />\n熟悉電影業運作的影評人畢明指，發行商以往都會以各種原因更改上映期，情況並非罕見，可能是「與院商傾唔掂數」，現階段較難猜測原因，但不排除與政治因素有關。<br />\n<br />\n畢明舉例指，以往《十年》和紀錄片《消失的檔案》都被「明言或心照」地被妨礙上映，即使《返校》將來能上映，戲院亦可能安排「天地場」或在偏遠地區戲院上映。<br />\n<br />\n遭大陸封殺<br />\n<br />\n該部電影講述暴政，畢明說：「香港、台灣同氣連枝，如果咁多嘢搵到共同點，應該好多香港人想睇。」畢明認為，若發行商背景屬親建制，出自政治考慮而延遲上映並不出奇。<br />\n<br />\n電影在大陸亦遭封殺，不但電影網站搜索不到該片資訊，網友在大陸社交論壇「討論」該片，也被封鎖刪除，觸碰到大陸敏感區。有網友在大陸問答社群「知乎」發帖討論《返校》，結果被網站以「違反相關法律法規」為由刪除。台灣方面，則有韓國瑜支持者認為電影是「政治操作」，呼籲抵制。"},{"pid":"f44299a53a34785771a0dd01e9ee8bcd450f8ac2","tid":1591943,"uid":31370,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"韓國魚說不的就更加要去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0db931a7036498dade87a9cac7143a8a812a794","tid":1591943,"uid":226048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:31:03.000Z","msg":"正啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等好耐"},{"pid":"ba1516803f02d61cedb8882eb86a3867df57e8e1","tid":1591943,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":